# Disable Auto Fullstop

Ref: https://osxdaily.com/2019/03/27/disable-period-typing-shortcut-mac/

1. Go to the ï£¿ Apple menu and choose "System Preferences"
1. Select the "Keyboard" preference panel, then choose the "Text" tab
1. Locate the setting for "Add period with double-space" and toggle the checkbox to the OFF position
